1407
01:12:27.600 --> 01:12:32.100
<font color="#00ffff">Wer von Ihnen weiss, was das ist?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Niemand?</font>

1408
01:12:32.760 --> 01:12:35.630
<font color="#00ffff">Ich frage das Publikum. Grüne</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Karte, wenn man weiss, was das ist.</font>

