1413
01:12:51.190 --> 01:12:54.230
<font color="#00ffff">Wer weiss es?</font>
<font color="#008000">- Ah, dieses Game.</font>

1414
01:12:54.930 --> 01:12:57.510
<font color="#00ffff">Sie hier drüben weiss es.</font>

